Description: Fragment of handle of East Greek pottery krater; 'metallic', twisted, ring handle pendent from ribbed 'spool'; broken off at top and back. Streakily glazed.
Curator's comments: Probably from the same vessel as 1965,0930.470.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GG.994)
